		<td><b>Re: How many milliamps on the +5vDC line?</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I measured the current draw FROM the 5v regulator at one point.  Don't remember what it was off the top of my head how much it was.  If you diligently search my posts I think you'll find it.  I only found a post where I claimed 'couple hundred mA' which is about what I would expect from the 5v line.  I've actually still got a jumper installed to measure it again if needed that bad, being a little lazy at the moment and don't feel like taking the screws out to gain access and remeasure it...<br /><br />As for voltage I have ran my NES down to 3.3v without issue, it started to freeze around 3.15-3.2V.  The colors are darker though when running at lowered voltages.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
